# Test HTTP Request File
# This file tests syntax highlighting for .http files

### Simple GET Request
GET https://api.github.com/users/octocat

### GET with Headers
GET https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts/1
Accept: application/json
User-Agent: REST-Client/1.0
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### POST Request with JSON Body
POST https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Post",
  "body": "This is a test",
  "userId": 1,
  "active": true,
  "count": 42,
  "metadata": null
}

### PUT Request with Variables
PUT https://api.example.com/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{$guid}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{userName}}",
  "timestamp": "{{$timestamp}}",
  "updated": true
}

### DELETE Request
DELETE https://api.example.com/posts/123
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

// This is also a comment
// Multiple comment styles are supported

### Request with Query Parameters
GET https://api.example.com/search?q={{searchTerm}}&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### PATCH Request
PATCH https://api.example.com/users/456 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "active"
}

/* Block comment
   Multiple lines
   Also supported */

### OPTIONS Request
OPTIONS https://api.example.com/resource
